Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there's an awesome\Ntreasure at the end of this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whoever gets it can be King\Nof the Pirates! Isn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unheard-of adventures are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage! Let that shred of courage grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horizons everyone\Ndreamed of were separate at first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now they can be seen\Nthrough a single telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bitter compass of destiny\Nis leading your heart astray
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so turn the wheel in the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss aside your bonds and your past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can surely smile despite that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears shed trying to achieve\Nyour dreams aren't for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.86,0:01:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Nami were stranded at God's Shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eneru's ship is too far from the top\Nof this vine. What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.12,0:01:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can we get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there some way?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:02:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the meantime, Eneru had\Nfinally found the golden bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Splendid!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.14,0:02:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the grand belfry that was the\Npride of the legendary city, Shandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, who had devised a plan, sent\Na message to Usopp and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? There's something written on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Cut down this huge vine\Nso it falls towards the west."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Eneru's final attack was imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've accomplished all my objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left now is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to destroy this land together with\Nthe cumuloregalis clouds using Raigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:03:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set off for the Endless Vearth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reject!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Break! Giant Jack!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes! Get on, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run it at full power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's insolent of you to try and come to me!\NYou need to be taught a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamaragan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:04:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Miracle on God's Land! The Love\NSong That Reached the Angels"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upper Yard is... being pulverized.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!! Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he doesn't want to come\Nin contact with you ever again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.27,0:04:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ruins are being exposed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He intends to pulverize the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wyper's lying on the ground down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro, too! That son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ruins...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless, Eneru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't bring down...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wyper!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the history of the proud warriors\Nwho lived in the land of Shandora.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where it is, this grand power\Nis strong, creates and nurtures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.67,0:05:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just can't bring it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many forests you burn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many ruins you destroy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The land won't be beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Get out of there, Wyper!\N--It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wyper's gonna die! Let me go, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? I can still hear driveling from below.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vearth is... That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not sinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upper Yard wasn't affected at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What great power!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Vearth is so grand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vearth wasn't something to fight over,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the blood of many people\Nwas shed, and many lives were lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:08:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't we notice it for 400 years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wyper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wyper!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out! The vine is falling!\NCome over here, now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Straw Hat!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:32.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"God"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!! Eneru!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're a bunch of...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over... the golden bell!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of this! I'm sick of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is big enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:52.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"God"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear with the land!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'll let your help go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship is that way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! There's an eddy of air\Nand lightning in there!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what'll happen to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do before this\Nhuge power, rubber man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Fi... re... works!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Peony!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you use thunder to create\Nbad weather for the idyllic sky islands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lightning freak!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this abnormal electric discharge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...! He has gold, which\Ncan transmit electricity, on his hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, all I have to do is drop it before\Nthe electricity completely discharges!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything... be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain McKinley! Please stop.\NThis is God's Land. It's pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if there's no point!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing else humans can do\Nwhen the situation is life or death!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to survive,\Nwe chose to abandon our land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we've lost a place to\Nreturn to and our way forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that we can do is pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we hear the "island's\Nsinging voice," this battle will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if no one will survive at this point...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if, had I had the\Ncourage to stand up to Eneru,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have had to involve those people...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Suu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if God exists?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he does, I wonder if he'd save us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:13:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... if you really exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.12,0:13:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...please protect them! God!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... make a miracle happen!\NProtect this land! God!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.14,0:14:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mass of thunderclouds has disappeared!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Ring the "fire of Shandora"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us hear the singing voice of the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you destroy Raigo?!\NYou monkey from the Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll ring you as well!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:32.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"God"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You insolent brat!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,200 Million Volt...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Amaru!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, you said?! You mean the golden bell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time it rings,\Nit will be the end of the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to hang onto such a legend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am God!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are just a Paramythia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that I can't\Ncrush you with my Logia power!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it doesn't work on me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of this "I'm God" crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What god wouldn't save anything at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You grabbed hold of it\Nto avoid being skewered, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do, rubber man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ow, ow, it's hot! Ouch!\N--You have nowhere to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pull of your arm will make the spear\Ndig deeper and deeper into you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, if you get away, you'll fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done well to climb up this high!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this is the end\Nof you and this land, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can create another Raigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our citizens' duty... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:18:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... are the sky islands...\Ngoing to disappear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you chose to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What're you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me, earlobes!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Rocket!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the bell rings!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll skewer you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:19:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Rifle!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too fast!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you return to Jaya, what will\Nyou think when you see we're gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a little longer! I'll let you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that "we are here"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light the fire of Shandora!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 400 years since\Nthe battle in the sky started.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just once, we wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.21,0:20:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. The sacred ground will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...sing again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...someday, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six years ago, I saw a giant city of gold\Non the Grand Line island of Jaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city of gold does exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:21:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one in history's ever disproved\Nthe city of gold or the sky island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what romanticism is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reach!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.11,0:21:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old guy! Can you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city of gold is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For 400 years, the city of gold\Nhas been here all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the sky!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're feeling lonely, talk to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gaze at the heavens\Nas you wander about
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the moon,\Nyou keep your gaze constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your deep reflection wanes\Nas you slowly disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.84,0:22:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay as you are, let those words guide you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.02,0:22:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream, you travelers who spend\Ncountless nights drifting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you may not be able to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.53,0:22:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will surely start moving forward again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:23:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear the bell. This is romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the story was a meaningless\Nfantasy and I'd forgotten about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.72,0:23:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is only one bell in\Nthis world that echoes this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.06,0:23:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city of gold was in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.39,0:23:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noland wasn't... My ancestor wasn't a liar!!
